{"tid":238425,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Working Holiday 噩耗！果園測試機械人取代人手採摘水果","createTime":"2017-05-11T04:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T12:00:36.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a2f0f6333dcb1e552ed4e3402b295094bb94375","tid":238425,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:09:13.000Z","msg":"五月 9, 2017<br />\n不少到澳州工作假期的年輕人，都會考慮到農場或果園打工，因為人工待遇不錯，工作一段時間就可以賺取足夠金錢之後渡假。不過在機械人技術越來越進步的年代，果園的主人亦在考慮如何減低成本，其中一個方法就是以機械人取代農場工人採摘水果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機械人公司 Abundant 就發明了一部採摘蘋果的機械人，利用抽真空的方式採摘樹上的蘋果。Abundant 的創辦人 Dan Steere 表示，採摘蘋果機械人的原型機現正在澳州進行測試，現在恰好是當地採摘蘋果的季節。測試結果證明，原型機能夠準確地發現蘋果，然後將它們從樹上輕輕地摘下來並放在大箱子內。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/0509-4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F0509-4b.jpg&h=57fc8813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSteere 表示成效令人信服，期望未來將機械人實際應用到商業運作中。Abundant 會在今年秋天在美國等多個地方繼續測試，目標是在明年生產多臂款式提升效率。Steere 指採摘蘋果或梨子的機械人過去已經有人研究過，不過最大難度還是靠機械人識別水果並採集，如果能夠在這方面作出突破，未來就可以達到 24 小時全自動機械人水果採摘了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/05/09/fruit-picking-robot/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F05%2F09%2Ffruit-picking-robot%2Flife-tech%2F&d=YX1qj72dVL8lCt3J0nVEUjANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=66c79644\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/05/09/fruit-picking-robot/life-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"1b291629401e867b2eaa4fa1c28f6fc25c1e3c11","tid":238425,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T06:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d083d76d8e497a07d343afcb2800ef644a6c7fe2","tid":238425,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T02:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394b0b1d1a6f316e132cc417de186eb8e8f1832b","tid":238425,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}